oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Baker, W. F., 1871 February 25
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of W. F. Baker, State of Tennessee, Davidson County, dated January 3rd, 1871. Illustrates the first page of the document. The notation reads: “Recorded in Book of Wills and Inventories No. 21, Page 689.” Another notation cites the date of Feby. 25, Term ’71. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
